[INAUDIBLE] bank.

00:27:11.980 --> 00:27:15.235
All you need to do, this is
the objective of this bank.

00:27:15.235 --> 00:27:16.600
This is how it is done.

00:27:16.600 --> 00:27:18.550
Repeatedly it has
been proven women

00:27:18.550 --> 00:27:20.710
are paying-- men and
women both are paying back

00:27:20.710 --> 00:27:22.360
payment is not a problem.

00:27:22.360 --> 00:27:23.620
And it's a sustainable.

00:27:23.620 --> 00:27:25.880
All the branches
of Grameen America

00:27:25.880 --> 00:27:29.050
right here, which is the most
expensive country in the world,

00:27:29.050 --> 00:27:30.014
they cover the cost.

00:27:30.014 --> 00:27:31.180
They cover the operational--

00:27:31.180 --> 00:27:32.221
JACK HIDARY: Sustainable.

00:27:32.221 --> 00:27:34.050
MUHAMMAD YUNUS:
Everything is sustainable.

