00:27:55.830 --> 00:27:57.940
Pawn shops all over the country.

00:27:57.940 --> 00:27:59.190
So this is a kind of mismatch.

00:27:59.190 --> 00:28:01.500
We don't understand why
people do in one way

00:28:01.500 --> 00:28:03.070
